'''埃莉諾·蘭伯特'''（{{lang-en|'''Eleanor Lambert Berkson'''}}）（{{bd|1903年|08月10日|2003年|10月7日}}）是[[纽约时装周|紐約時裝週]]的創辦人，美國時尚界及公關界的核心人物。<ref name="Stahl Case Study: Eleanor Lambert Demand Creator">{{Cite web|url=http://www.valuewalk.com/2013/11/eleanor-lambert-demand-creator/|title=Stahl Case Study: Eleanor Lambert Demand Creator|accessdate=20 November 2013|date=18 November 2013|publisher=[[ValueWalk|ValueWalk]] LLC}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny">{{Cite web|url=http://www.cfda.com/about/history#!|title=Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny|accessdate=20 November 2013|author=Tiffany,  John|publisher=Council of Fashion Designers of America|archive-date=2018-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210215542/https://cfda.com/about/history#!|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/914905/Eleanor-Lambert|title=Eleanor Lambert|accessdate=20 November 2013|publisher=Encyclopaedia Britannica|archive-date=2015-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502230643/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/914905/Eleanor-Lambert|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Eleanor Lambert, Empress of Fashion, Dies at 100">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/10/08/nyregion/eleanor-lambert-empress-of-fashion-dies-at-100.html|title=Eleanor Lambert, Empress of Fashion, Dies at 100|accessdate=21 November 2013|author=NEMY, ENID|date=October 8, 2003|publisher=The New York Times|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118045728/https://www.nytimes.com/2003/10/08/nyregion/eleanor-lambert-empress-of-fashion-dies-at-100.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 個人生平 ==
蘭伯特出生於[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]]的[[克劳福兹维尔_(印第安纳州)|克劳福兹维尔]]，<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" /><ref name="Eleanor Of Seventh Avenue: Where Fashion Week Came From">{{Cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/gioia-diliberto/eleanor-of-seventh-avenue_b_268619.html|title=Eleanor Of Seventh Avenue: Where Fashion Week Came From|accessdate=20 November 2013|author=Diliberto, Gioia|date=2009-09-09|publisher=Huffington Post|archive-date=2016-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617113855/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/gioia-diliberto/eleanor-of-seventh-avenue_b_268619.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>於{{link-en|約翰·赫倫藝術學院|John Herron School of Art}}及[[芝加哥藝術學院|芝加哥藝術學院]]進修[[時裝|時裝]]。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" /><ref name="Eleanor Of Seventh Avenue: Where Fashion Week Came From" />蘭伯特渴望成為一名雕塑家，卻進了廣告行業。<ref name="Telegraph10Oct2003">{{Cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1443712/Eleanor-Lambert.html|title=Eleanor Lambert Obituary|accessdate=20 November 2013|date=10 October 2003|publisher=The Telegraph newspaper|archive-date=2019-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010144229/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1443712/Eleanor-Lambert.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在曼哈頓從事[[廣告代理商|廣告代理]]，主要為藝術家以及藝術畫廊服務。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" /><ref name="Eleanor Of Seventh Avenue: Where Fashion Week Came From" />

她有過兩段婚姻：20世紀20年代，與第一任丈夫'''威爾斯·康納'''（{{lang-en|Wills Conner}}）結婚。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert, Empress of Fashion, Dies at 100" />1936年離婚後，與第二任丈夫'''西摩爾·伯克森'''（{{lang-en|Seymour Berkson}}）<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" />結婚，直至1959年西摩爾逝世。<ref name="Telegraph10Oct2003"/>她與西摩爾育有一個兒子，是著名詩人{{link-en|比爾·伯克森|Bill Berkson}}。<ref name="Telegraph10Oct2003"/>2003年10月7日，埃莉諾·蘭伯特於紐約市曼哈頓逝世。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert, Empress of Fashion, Dies at 100" />

