20世紀30年代中期，蘭伯特作為[[惠特尼美术馆|惠特尼美术馆]]首席媒體總監協助建立了[[現代藝術博物館|現代藝術博物館]]（MoMA），<ref name="Stahl Case Study: Eleanor Lambert Demand Creator"/><ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" /><ref name="Eleanor Of Seventh Avenue: Where Fashion Week Came From" />展出了包括[[杰克逊·波洛克|傑克遜·波洛克]]、{{link-en|雅各布·愛潑斯坦|Jacob Epstein}}、[[野口勇|野口勇]]為代表的眾多藝術家的作品。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" /><ref name="Eleanor Of Seventh Avenue: Where Fashion Week Came From" />

20世紀40年代，蘭伯特創立了「'''{{link-en|國際最佳着裝名單|International Best Dressed List}}'''」，1943年創立了「'''{{link-en|科蒂美國時尚評論家獎|Coty Award}}'''」，發起[[纽约时装周|紐約時裝週]]。<ref name="Stahl Case Study: Eleanor Lambert Demand Creator"/><ref name="Eleanor Of Seventh Avenue: Where Fashion Week Came From" /><ref name="time">{{Cite web|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2110513_2110630_2110690,00.html|title=Eleanor Lambert|accessdate=20 November 2013|author=Skarda, Erin|date=April 2, 2012|publisher=Time magazine|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803100318/https://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2110513_2110630_2110690,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Author to Discuss Fashion Industry Impresario Eleanor Lambert, Feb. 2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2012/12-004.html|title=Author to Discuss Fashion Industry Impresario Eleanor Lambert, Feb. 2|accessdate=20 November 2013|date=January 3, 2012|publisher=Library of Congress|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417064452/http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2012/12-004.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1959年及1967年，[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]安排她到俄羅斯、德國、義大利、澳洲、日本、英國以及瑞士推廣美國時尚文化。<ref name="Stahl Case Study: Eleanor Lambert Demand Creator"/><ref name="time"/>

1962年，蘭伯特成立{{link-en|美國時裝設計師協會|Council of Fashion Designers of America}}（縮寫：{{lang|en|CFDA}}），是CFDA終身榮譽會員。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" />1965年，蘭伯特被[[林登·约翰逊|約翰遜]]總統任命為「{{link-en|國家藝術基金會|National Endowment for the Arts}}」的「{{link-en|國家藝術組織|National Council on the Arts}}」成員。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" />

2001年，CFDA創立“埃莉諾·蘭伯特獎”（{{lang-en|The Eleanor Lambert Award}}），用以表彰對世界時尚行業作出傑出貢獻的人。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" />

在她去世前幾個月，蘭伯特將“{{link-en|國際最佳着裝名單|International Best Dressed List}}”交給了[[名利场_(杂志)|名利場]]的四位編輯。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" />2003年9月，蘭伯特於2004春夏紐約時裝週公開露面後不久逝世，享嵩壽100歲。<ref name="Eleanor Lambert believed in destiny" /><ref name="Eleanor Lambert grave">{{Cite web|url=http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&GRid=7959373|title=Eleanor Lambert (1903-2003)|accessdate=21 November 2013|author=Moody, Ron|date=October 8, 2003|publisher=Find a Grave.com|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122223302/http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&GRid=7959373|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的孫子摩西·伯克森（{{lang-en|Moses Berkson}}）在她去世後拍了一部關於蘭伯特的[[紀錄片|紀錄片]]《埃莉諾——美國時尚教母》（{{Lang-en|Eleanor - Godmother of American Fashion}}）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://vimeo.com/74978706|title=Eleanor - Godmother of American Fashion|accessdate=2016-11-22|author=Moses Berkson|date=|work=Vimeo|publisher=|quote=A short documentary film I directed about my Grandmother, Eleanor Lambert.|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122223218/https://vimeo.com/74978706|dead-url=no}}</ref>

